{"TopicId":163111,"ForumId":29,"TopicTitle":"[HELP!] Read CFG files?","CreatedByName":"Xyphos","CreatedById":139010,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-10T21:08:44Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Xyphos","CreatedById":139010,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-10T21:08:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI wanna import data from a config file and have it instanced as a class object, but I don\u0027t know how.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nC# Code:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cpre class=\u0022ipsCode prettyprint lang-c prettyprinted\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022kwd\u0022\u003Epublic\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022kwd\u0022\u003Eclass\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EMyClass\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E{\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E\n\t\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022kwd\u0022\u003Epublic\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003Eint\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EMyInt\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E;\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E\n\t\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022kwd\u0022\u003Epublic\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022kwd\u0022\u003Ebool\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EMyBool\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E;\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E}\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E\n\nvar myClass \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E=\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E iDontKnowHow\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E\u0026lt;\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EMyClass\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E\u0026gt;.\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EReadFromConfigFile\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E(\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003EfileName\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E);\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/pre\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCFG File:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cpre class=\u0022ipsCode\u0022\u003E\nMYCLASS {\n\tMyBool = false\n\tMyInt = 1337\n}\u003C/pre\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-10T21:20:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRead up on config nodes\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xyphos","CreatedById":139010,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-10T21:26:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223116961\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022163111\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221499721652\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129964\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022linuxgurugamer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 minutes ago, linuxgurugamer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRead up on config nodes\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nlink to source? I learn best hands-on, never from manuals.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-10T21:41:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223116963\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022163111\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221499721960\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022139010\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Xyphos\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 minutes ago, Xyphos said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nlink to source? I learn best hands-on, never from manuals.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUmmm, almost any mod?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut, here is an example:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/linuxgurugamer/PatchManager/blob/master/PatchManager/PatchManager.cs#L300-L374\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://github.com/linuxgurugamer/PatchManager/blob/master/PatchManager/PatchManager.cs#L300-L374\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HebaruSan","CreatedById":156657,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-10T21:41:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Col\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nHave MyClass inherit from MonoBehaviour\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nApply the [Persistent] attribute to the properties you want to have set\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nCall ConfigNode.Load to get a ConfigNode object from the file path\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nCall\u00A0\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#24292e;\u0022\u003EConfigNode.LoadObjectFromConfig to set that object\u0027s properties to your object\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nExample:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/HebaruSan/SmartTank/blob/master/src/Settings.cs\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://github.com/HebaruSan/SmartTank/blob/master/src/Settings.cs\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n(Ignore\u00A0HideNonProceduralPartsChanged, it\u0027s specific to that mod)\u003Cbr\u003E\n(Also uses string interpolation from C# 6 on line 34; you can just hard code the file path if you prefer.)\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-07-10T21:49:24Z\u0022 title=\u002207/10/2017 09:49  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 10, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by HebaruSan\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EUse pre-Websterian spelling\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xyphos","CreatedById":139010,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-10T21:46:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDomo arigato Herbaru-San. - that\u0027s just what I needed to learn from.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}